<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="IE=edge">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>New Profile</title>
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="/styles/base.css">
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="/styles/profiles.css">
</head>
<body>
  <main id="new-user">
    <form action="/profiles" method="POST" enctype="multipart/form-data"><!--양식제출 기본값(application/x-www-form-urlencoded) / multipart... : 하나 이상의 파일 선택기가 포함된 양식이 있는경우 사용-->
      <div class="form-control">
        <label for="username">Username</label>
        <input type="text" id="username" name="username" required>
      </div>
      <div class="form-control">
        <label for="image">User image</label>
        <input type="file" id="image" name="image" required accept="image/jpg,image/png"> <!--파일선택기를 둘수 있음, required: 파일없으면 경고-->
      </div>
      <button class="btn">Save User</button>
    </form>
  </main>
</body>
</html>